{"tid":1021454,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"苟芸慧貼身服務送老公","createTime":"2019-02-14T09:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T14:17:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2b913aac5feb4c9894f6b3c8dc10673826a408","tid":1021454,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:12:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190214/20612332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F20612332&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=fc48cbda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F20612332&h=b6b8e6aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190214/20612332</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月14日 <br />\n<br />\n苟芸慧貼身服務送老公<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190214/large/14ec2p30e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190214%2Flarge%2F14ec2p30e.jpg&h=93e3645a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n苟芸慧指今日情人節由老公話事，會貼身照顧對方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n苟芸慧昨日於中環出席護膚品牌活動，她自言今年是婚後首度派利是，既開心又興奮，還笑言很榮幸被稱陸太，經常被親友催生豬B。提到今日情人節，她說：「老公book咗食飯，二人世界，今年身份唔同咗，其實好開心，終於以陸太身份同陸生慶祝。」問她送甚麼給丈夫？她說：「係私人全套服務，由朝早起身開始，貼身照顧，老公乜都唔使做，想點就點。佢物質上乜都有，想畀心意上嘅嘢佢。」<br />\n<br />\n問到太甜蜜會否有「意外」發生？苟芸慧笑說：「老公堅持嘅一定做到，我哋諗定生虎B，老公都想自己做小朋友，因為佢知道有咗小朋友我就唔理佢，𠵱家享受二人世界先。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：羅慧敏<br />\n攝影：陳慧安  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n青雲首次謝票好緊張<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n王晶否認帶女上房"},{"pid":"cc2175866f8f9e66928f6c9287181688b9662fad","tid":1021454,"uid":236288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/